# Semgrep's supply-chain pack (p/ci) flags these config files against opinionated defaults that
# this repo addresses deliberately:
#   - minimumReleaseAge IS set (1440m) in pnpm-workspace.yaml; pnpm 11 no longer reads it from .npmrc.
#   - build scripts are deny-by-default via `allowBuilds` (only prisma/nx compile at install).
#   - .npmrc is an intentional empty placeholder kept so the Dockerfile `COPY .npmrc*` layer matches.
# App source is still fully scanned — only these two config files are excluded.
.npmrc
pnpm-workspace.yaml
